  "title": "Relief Teacher",
  "description": "<p><u>Employer: Grace Orchard School</u></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Carry out lessons as planned by the class teacher (teaching package provided)</li><li>Monitor and maintain the discipline of the class that you are teaching</li><li>Help ensure a safe and stimulating educational environment for students</li><li>Assist students, individually or in groups, with lesson assignments and projects</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum ‘A’ level/Diploma</li><li>Passion in teaching pupils with special needs</li><li>Those with relevant experience but without the necessary qualifications will be considered on a case-by-case basis.</li></ul>",
